Module se1.bestellsystem

Package datamodel

package datamodel
Package with data model classes for the se1.bestellsystem.

The package provides classes for entities and relations managed by the order processing application.

Version:
"D12-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT"
Author:
"sgraupner"
  • Class
    Description
    Article
    Immutable entity class representing an Article, which is a product referred to in orders.
    Customer
    Immutable entity class representing a Customer, a person who creates and holds (owns) orders in the system.
    DataFactory
    Factory class with create()-methods to instantiate objects of classes of the datamodel package from validated parameters.
    Order
    Immutable entity class representing an Order, which is a collection of Article items purchased by a Customer.
    Order.OrderItem
    Record of an order line item comprised of a number of units order of one Article.
    Pricing
    Immutable class to store pricing information organized by Enum Pricing.PricingCategory with:
    Pricing.Country
    Enum or countries with currencies used.
    Pricing.Currency
    Enum of currency with three-letter code and Unicode symbol.
    Pricing.PricingCategory
    Enum of pricing categories
    Pricing.TAXRate
    Enum of TAXRates for Article instances.
